rawContent:
@CLASSIFIEDok Hey Daniel! We have a workaround below.
Press XBOX button on controller
Highlight GRB.
Press option button on controller
Selected Manage game & addons
Select Saved Data option
Delete gamer tag save (Selected "from everywhere")
Delete reserved data
Restart the game
